HEADWORD: Hedge fund
<hw>Hedge" fund`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Finance)</fld>
<def>a mutual fund or partnership of investors who pool large sums of
money to speculate in securities, increasing the risk of such activity
by using borrowed money to leverage the investments, or by selling
short.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

